A '''honey do list''' is a request or potentially a collection of [[requests]], usually by a [[spouse]] for someone to perform a series of [[task]]s, [[assignment]]s or jobs dealing with the operations of a [[household]], e.g. a [[wife]] asking a [[husband]] to clean out the [[garage]], repair a broken [[window]], install a household hardware [[device]] such as a [[garbage disposal]] or [[dishwasher]], etc.  Comes from the [[stereotype|stereotypical]] method of asking for the [[work]] to be done, such as ''Honey would you do this for me, I'd like you to..'', or ''Honey, do me a favor, and...''